import React from 'react'
import{Wrapper, OverlayWrapper, Card, CardBody, CardImage, CardPrice, cardTitle, CardTitle,}from "./Styles";

export default function Product(){
    return
       <Wrapper>
           <Card>
                <CardImage src={props.imageURL}/>
                <CardBody>
                    <CardTitle>{props.title}</CardTitle>
                    <CardPrice>{props.title}</CardPrice>
                </CardBody>
           </Card>
       </Wrapper>;
    
}
